survey_response.review_text:
Doctors ar very friendly and professional.
They check on every interval if we are comfortable with the treatment, or if we need a break. They explain the process post the treatment is started, and once they complete the treatment they let us know on what needs to be followed 
until our next sitting.
Efficiently carried out the root canal procedure.  Literally 0 wait time in both sessions so far.  Experience post RCT is good so far.
Good to come for the treatment . But little expensive we are feeling.we are a long term customer for this hospital too.
Treatment is good so whenever dental problems comes will come here mainly root canal I have done.good

Honestly I was really sceptical about RCT treatment, but once I met Dr. Uday I was pretty sure that I am in safe hands. He not only discussed my oral health issues but also elaborated about the overall process and steps to keep the teeth in a healthy state. I would definitely recommend Dr. Uday for not only RCT treatment but also other dental related issues.

I have been a patient of Dr. Kamath for many years. He is an excellent doctor, very experienced, and I trust him very much. This time too, even though Koramangala is quite a distance for us , I wanted to get it treated by him only. I would highly recommend Dr. Kamath to anyone who has a tooth problem.

I was getting my first dental procedure done and it was a root canal. Was pretty apprehensive about how painful it could be. Doctor was extremely professional and calm and that put me at ease immediately. It all went smoothly with no pain at all. Would definitely recommend him to anyone who wants to be sure when they go to a dentist.

Dr. Kamath explained the diagnosis and the possible treatment options very well. I didn't experience much pain during the multiple sessions of Root Canal Treatment procedure. He kept explaining what is being done in each session. He was very courteous and friendly in nature. I hardly took any pain killer or antibiotic after each session.

my wife is in need of tooth replacement. Dr. Kamath had explained the need and procedure of the treatment very precisely. he was very friendly and gave genuine suggestions. the treatment is very satisfactory. he takes follow up every now and then.  my wife is all smiles now. highly recommended.

It’s the comfortable and friendly environment at the clinic which made me feel more confident and happy rather than being anxious and scared.
Dr Uday Kamath, Dr Pramod and Dr Meghna was friendly and helped me overcome my fear as it was my first RCT.
They explained clearly what the issue and how long the process will take. 
One of the best dental care clinic.
